          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_4369937061961780800.png",
                "id": "talent62542",
                "key": "炎舞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "炎舞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，随机<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">热情护盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/8d7c3ccfcbf19d97fbdca9cfb97e2f06_4285528936457016510.png",
                "id": "talent78373",
                "key": "热情拂扫",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "热情拂扫"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>；<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>我方所有手牌，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">氛围烈焰</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/ced1684d4cd585b037e648715a22367e_5723083768826773362.png",
                "id": "talent3340",
                "key": "叛逆刮弦",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "叛逆刮弦"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超载</span>：本伤害<span>+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span><span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_8238052868056544371.png",
                "id": "talent75699",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">热情护盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>为我方出战角色提供2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">氛围烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方宣布结束时：</span>如果我方的手牌数量不多于1，则造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2330531930016844792.png",
